thread.title_full: BRIEF-Seamless Distribution says wins African order worth $2.4 mln | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Seamless Distribution says wins African order worth $2.4 mln
text:
Oct 2 Seamless Distribution AB
* Says wins order for proprietary hand worth $2.4 million
* Says, in total, Seamless has received orders valued at $5.3 million in Africa Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Stockholm Newsroom)
